headline: SpaceX Just Made Elon Musk $20 Billion Richer
summary: SpaceX has a new valuation, according to Bloomberg.  The $50 billion increase makes Musk about $20 billion richer, as he is thought to hold some 40% of SpaceX stock.  Musk’s total stake in SpaceX is worth about $160 billion.
